Description: Load Bragg grating waveguide vertices from a TXT file and draw

Input: file with the format: (x1,y1,x2,y2;...)
which can be generated in Matlab by:
  co = co / dbu;
  fid=fopen(file,'w');
  fprintf(fid,'(');
  fprintf(fid,'%d,%d;',round(co));
  fprintf(fid,')');
  fclose(fid);
